between agents only not set rule or process, 

Confirm your understanding.

Body:
DROP VIEW JMBAXIFAS.GST_PURCHASE_REGISTER;

/* Formatted on 10/18/2019 3:46:51 PM (QP5 v5.115.810.9015) */

CREATE OR REPLACE FORCE VIEW JMBAXIFAS.GST_PURCHASE_REGISTER

(

 TXN_ID,

 TXN_TYPE_ID,

 LOCATION_ID,

 ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

 VOUCHER_NO,

 VOUCHER_DT,

 ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID,

 LEDGER_NAME,

 INVOICE_NUMBER,

 BILL_DATE,

 DEPT_CODE,

 DEPT_NAME,

 INV_BASIC_AMOUNT,

 TDS_AMOUNT,

 INV_AMOUNT,

 AGENT_ID,

 DOCUMENT_TYPE,

 DOCUMENT_STATUS,

 JMB_GSTN_NO,

 JMB_STATE_CODE,

 JMB_STATE_NAME,

 GST_AUTO_ID,

 VENDOR_STATE_CODE,

 VENDOR_GSTN_NO,

 VENDOR_BILL_TYPE,

 VENDOR_SEZ_FLAG,

 REG_OR_UNREG,

 CR_INV_DOC_REF,

 AGNST_INV_NUMBER,

 AGNST_INV_DATE,

 GROUP_ID

)

AS

 SELECT  FM.TXN_ID,

      FM.TXN_TYPE_ID,

      FM.LOCATION_ID,

      FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

      FM.DOCUMENT_REF_NO AS VOUCHER_NO,

      FM.TXN_DATE AS VOUCHER_DT,

      FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID,

      FAM.DESCRIPTION AS LEDGER_NAME,

      FOD.INVOICE_NUMBER,

      FOD.BILL_DATE,

      FOD.DEPT_CODE,

      DM.DEPT_NAME,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) AS INV_BASIC_AMOUNT,

      NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS TDS_AMOUNT,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) + NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS INV_AMOUNT,

      AM.AGENT_ID,

      'RI' AS DOCUMENT_TYPE,

      'O' AS DOCUMENT_STATUS,

      reg.GSTN_NO AS JMB_GSTN_NO,

      REG.STATE_CODE AS JMB_STATE_CODE,

      REG.STATE_NAME AS JMB_STATE_NAME,

      FOD.GST_AUTO_ID,

      GSTD.STATE_CODE AS VENDOR_STATE_CODE,

      FOD.GSTN_NO AS VENDOR_GSTN_NO,

      FOD.INVOICE_TYPE AS VENDOR_BILL_TYPE,

      DECODE (FOD.SEZ_FLAG, 1, 'Y', 'N') AS VENDOR_SEZ_FLAG,

      FOD.REG_UNREG_TYPE AS REG_OR_UNREG,

      '' AS CR_INV_DOC_REF,

      '' AS AGNST_INV_NUMBER,

      NULL AS AGNST_INV_DATE,

      GM.GROUP_ID

  FROM  FA_TXN_MASTER FM,

      FA_TXN_DETAIL FD,

      FA_TXN_OPS_DETAIL FOD,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_MASTER FAM,

      fa_dept_master dm,

      AGENT_MASTER AM,

      ( SELECT  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID,

            SUM (NVL (AMOUNT / 100, 0)) AS TDS_AMOUNT

        FROM  FA_TXN_DETAIL TEMP

        WHERE  TEMP.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IN

               ( SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID FROM TDS_SLABS_MASTER)

            AND TEMP.AMOUNT > 0

      GROUP BY  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID) FD1,

      GST_REG_NOS reg,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_GST_DTL GSTD,

      fa_sub_group_master sg,

      fa_group_master gm,

      fa_category_master cm

  WHERE    FM.TXN_ID = FD.TXN_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.TXN_ID = FOD.TXN_ID

      AND FD.TXN_TYPE_ID = FOD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FD.LOCATION_ID = FOD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FOD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.SERIAL_NO = FOD.SERIAL_NO

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID = FOD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID = FAM.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND FOD.DEPT_CODE = DM.DEPT_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = AM.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID IN ('PBK', 'ADM', 'SCI')

      AND FAM.SUB_GROUP_ID = SG.SUB_GROUP_ID

      AND SG.GROUP_ID = GM.GROUP_ID

      AND GM.CATEGORY_ID = CM.CATEGORY_ID

      AND CM.CATEGORY_ID IN ('1', '2')

      AND SG.SUB_GROUP_ID NOT IN (96, 97, 98)

      AND FD.AMOUNT > 0

      AND FM.TXN_DATE >= TO_DATE ('01-JUL-2017', 'DD-MON-YYYY')

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID NOT IN

          (SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

            FROM  TDS_SLABS_MASTER

           WHERE  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IS NOT NULL)

      AND FM.TXN_ID = FD1.TXN_ID(+)

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD1.TXN_TYPE_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD1.LOCATION_ID(+)

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD1.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID(+)

      AND am.agent_id = reg.agent_id(+)

      AND FOD.GST_AUTO_ID = GSTD.GST_AUTO_ID(+)

      AND FOD.INVOICE_NUMBER NOT IN

          (SELECT  INVOICE_ID FROM GST_INVOICE_HDR)

 UNION ALL

 SELECT  FM.TXN_ID,

      FM.TXN_TYPE_ID,

      FM.LOCATION_ID,

      FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

      FM.DOCUMENT_REF_NO AS VOUCHER_NO,

      FM.TXN_DATE AS VOUCHER_DT,

      FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID,

      FAM.DESCRIPTION AS LEDGER_NAME,

      FOD.INVOICE_NUMBER,

      NVL (FOD.BILL_DATE, INVOICE_DT) BILL_DATE,

      FOD.DEPT_CODE,

      DM.DEPT_NAME,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) AS INV_BASIC_AMOUNT,

      NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS TDS_AMOUNT,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) + NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS INV_AMOUNT,

      AM.AGENT_ID,

      'RI' AS DOCUMENT_TYPE,

      'O' AS DOCUMENT_STATUS,

      reg.GSTN_NO AS JMB_GSTN_NO,

      REG.STATE_CODE AS JMB_STATE_CODE,

      REG.STATE_NAME AS JMB_STATE_NAME,

      NVL (FOD.GST_AUTO_ID, GIH.INV_GST_AUTO_ID) GST_AUTO_ID,

      REG1.STATE_CODE AS VENDOR_STATE_CODE,

      NVL (REG1.GSTN_NO, GSTD.GSTN_NO) AS VENDOR_GSTN_NO,

      FOD.INVOICE_TYPE AS VENDOR_BILL_TYPE,

      DECODE (FOD.SEZ_FLAG, 1, 'Y', 'N') AS VENDOR_SEZ_FLAG,

      FOD.REG_UNREG_TYPE AS REG_OR_UNREG,

      '' AS CR_INV_DOC_REF,

      '' AS AGNST_INV_NUMBER,

      NULL AS AGNST_INV_DATE,

      GM.GROUP_ID

  FROM  FA_TXN_MASTER FM,

      FA_TXN_DETAIL FD,

      FA_TXN_OPS_DETAIL FOD,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_MASTER FAM,

      fa_dept_master dm,

      AGENT_MASTER AM,

      ( SELECT  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID,

            SUM (NVL (AMOUNT / 100, 0)) AS TDS_AMOUNT

        FROM  FA_TXN_DETAIL TEMP

        WHERE  TEMP.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IN

               ( SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID FROM TDS_SLABS_MASTER)

            AND TEMP.AMOUNT > 0

      GROUP BY  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID) FD1,

      GST_REG_NOS reg,

      GST_REG_NOS reg1,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_GST_DTL GSTD,

      fa_sub_group_master sg,

      fa_group_master gm,

      fa_category_master cm,

      gst_invoice_hdr gih,

      USER_MASTER UM

  WHERE    FM.TXN_ID = FD.TXN_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.TXN_ID = FOD.TXN_ID

      AND FD.TXN_TYPE_ID = FOD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FD.LOCATION_ID = FOD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FOD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.SERIAL_NO = FOD.SERIAL_NO

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID = FOD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND DECODE (FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID, 293, 3728, FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID) =

         FAM.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND FOD.DEPT_CODE = DM.DEPT_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = AM.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID IN ('PBK', 'ADM', 'SCI')

      AND FAM.SUB_GROUP_ID = SG.SUB_GROUP_ID

      AND SG.GROUP_ID = GM.GROUP_ID

      AND GM.CATEGORY_ID = CM.CATEGORY_ID

      AND CM.CATEGORY_ID IN ('1', '2')

      AND SG.SUB_GROUP_ID NOT IN (96, 97, 98)

      AND FD.AMOUNT > 0

      AND FM.TXN_DATE >= TO_DATE ('01-JUL-2017', 'DD-MON-YYYY')

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID NOT IN

          (SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

            FROM  TDS_SLABS_MASTER

           WHERE  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IS NOT NULL)

      AND FM.TXN_ID = FD1.TXN_ID(+)

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD1.TXN_TYPE_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD1.LOCATION_ID(+)

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD1.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID(+)

      AND am.agent_id = reg.agent_id(+)

      AND FOD.INVOICE_NUMBER = GIH.INVOICE_ID

      AND gih.INV_GST_AUTO_ID = GSTD.GST_AUTO_ID(+)

      AND GIH.CREATED_BY = UM.USER_ID

      AND UM.AGENT_USER = REG1.AGENT_ID

 UNION ALL

 SELECT  FM.TXN_ID,

      FM.TXN_TYPE_ID,

      FM.LOCATION_ID,

      FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

      FM.DOCUMENT_REF_NO AS VOUCHER_NO,

      FM.TXN_DATE AS VOUCHER_DT,

      FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID,

      FAM.DESCRIPTION AS LEDGER_NAME,

      FOD.INVOICE_NUMBER,

      FOD.BILL_DATE,

      FOD.DEPT_CODE,

      DM.DEPT_NAME,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) AS INV_BASIC_AMOUNT,

      NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS TDS_AMOUNT,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) + NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS INV_AMOUNT,

      AM.AGENT_ID,

      'C' AS DOCUMENT_TYPE,

      'O' AS DOCUMENT_STATUS,

      reg.GSTN_NO AS JMB_GSTN_NO,

      REG.STATE_CODE AS JMB_STATE_CODE,

      REG.STATE_NAME AS JMB_STATE_NAME,

      FOD.GST_AUTO_ID,

      GSTD.STATE_CODE AS VENDOR_STATE_CODE,

      FOD.GSTN_NO AS VENDOR_GSTN_NO,

      FOD.INVOICE_TYPE AS VENDOR_BILL_TYPE,

      DECODE (FOD.SEZ_FLAG, '1', 'Y', 'N') AS VENDOR_SEZ_FLAG,

      FOD.REG_UNREG_TYPE AS REG_OR_UNREG,

      FOD.NARRATION AS CR_INV_DOC_REF,

      FTV.INVOICE_NUMBER AS AGNST_INV_NUMBER,

      FTV.BILL_DATE AS AGNST_INV_DATE,

      GM.GROUP_ID

  FROM  FA_TXN_MASTER FM,

      FA_TXN_DETAIL FD,

      FA_TXN_OPS_DETAIL FOD,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_MASTER FAM,

      fa_dept_master dm,

      AGENT_MASTER AM,

      ( SELECT  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID,

            SUM (NVL (AMOUNT / 100, 0)) AS TDS_AMOUNT

        FROM  FA_TXN_DETAIL TEMP

        WHERE  TEMP.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IN

               ( SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID FROM TDS_SLABS_MASTER)

            AND TEMP.AMOUNT < 0

      GROUP BY  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID) FD1,

      GST_REG_NOS reg,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_GST_DTL GSTD,

      fa_sub_group_master sg,

      fa_group_master gm,

      fa_category_master cm,

      (SELECT  DISTINCT DOCUMENT_REF_NO, INVOICE_NUMBER, BILL_DATE

       FROM  FA_TXN_VIEW) FTV

  WHERE    FM.TXN_ID = FD.TXN_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.TXN_ID = FOD.TXN_ID

      AND FD.TXN_TYPE_ID = FOD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FD.LOCATION_ID = FOD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FOD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.SERIAL_NO = FOD.SERIAL_NO

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID = FOD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID = FAM.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND FOD.DEPT_CODE = DM.DEPT_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = AM.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID IN ('VCN')

      AND FAM.SUB_GROUP_ID = SG.SUB_GROUP_ID

      AND SG.GROUP_ID = GM.GROUP_ID

      AND GM.CATEGORY_ID = CM.CATEGORY_ID

      AND CM.CATEGORY_ID IN ('1', '2')

      AND SG.SUB_GROUP_ID NOT IN (96, 97, 98)

      AND FD.AMOUNT < 0

      AND FM.TXN_DATE >= TO_DATE ('01-JUL-2017', 'DD-MON-YYYY')

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID NOT IN

          (SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

            FROM  TDS_SLABS_MASTER

           WHERE  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IS NOT NULL)

      AND FM.TXN_ID = FD1.TXN_ID(+)

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD1.TXN_TYPE_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD1.LOCATION_ID(+)

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD1.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID(+)

      AND am.agent_id = reg.agent_id(+)

      AND FOD.GST_AUTO_ID = GSTD.GST_AUTO_ID(+)

      AND FOD.NARRATION = FTV.DOCUMENT_REF_NO(+)

 UNION ALL

 SELECT  FM.TXN_ID,

      FM.TXN_TYPE_ID,

      FM.LOCATION_ID,

      FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

      FM.DOCUMENT_REF_NO AS VOUCHER_NO,

      FM.TXN_DATE AS VOUCHER_DT,

      FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID,

      FAM.DESCRIPTION AS LEDGER_NAME,

      FM.CROSS_REF,

      FTV.TXNSORTING,

      FOD.DEPT_CODE,

      DM.DEPT_NAME,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) AS INV_BASIC_AMOUNT,

      NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS TDS_AMOUNT,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) + NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS INV_AMOUNT,

      AM.AGENT_ID,

      'REV' AS DOCUMENT_TYPE,

      'O' AS DOCUMENT_STATUS,

      reg.GSTN_NO AS JMB_GSTN_NO,

      REG.STATE_CODE AS JMB_STATE_CODE,

      REG.STATE_NAME AS JMB_STATE_NAME,

      FOD.GST_AUTO_ID,

      GSTD.STATE_CODE AS VENDOR_STATE_CODE,

      FTV.GSTN_NO AS VENDOR_GSTN_NO,

      FOD.INVOICE_TYPE AS VENDOR_BILL_TYPE,

      DECODE (FOD.SEZ_FLAG, '1', 'Y', 'N') AS VENDOR_SEZ_FLAG,

      FOD.REG_UNREG_TYPE AS REG_OR_UNREG,

      FOD.NARRATION AS CR_INV_DOC_REF,

      '' AS AGNST_INV_NUMBER,

      NULL AS AGNST_INV_DATE,

      GM.GROUP_ID

  FROM  FA_TXN_MASTER FM,

      FA_TXN_DETAIL FD,

      FA_TXN_OPS_DETAIL FOD,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_MASTER FAM,

      fa_dept_master dm,

      AGENT_MASTER AM,

      ( SELECT  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID,

            SUM (NVL (AMOUNT / 100, 0)) AS TDS_AMOUNT

        FROM  FA_TXN_DETAIL TEMP

        WHERE  TEMP.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IN

               ( SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID FROM TDS_SLABS_MASTER)

            AND TEMP.AMOUNT < 0

      GROUP BY  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID) FD1,

      GST_REG_NOS reg,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_GST_DTL GSTD,

      fa_sub_group_master sg,

      fa_group_master gm,

      fa_category_master cm,

      (SELECT  DISTINCT DOCUMENT_REF_NO,

               INVOICE_NUMBER,

               txnsorting,

               GSTN_NO

       FROM  FA_TXN_VIEW

       WHERE  INVOICE_NUMBER IS NOT NULL) FTV

  WHERE    FM.TXN_ID = FD.TXN_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.TXN_ID = FOD.TXN_ID

      AND FD.TXN_TYPE_ID = FOD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FD.LOCATION_ID = FOD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FOD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.SERIAL_NO = FOD.SERIAL_NO

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID = FOD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID = FAM.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND FOD.DEPT_CODE = DM.DEPT_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = AM.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID IN ('RJV')

      AND FAM.SUB_GROUP_ID = SG.SUB_GROUP_ID

      AND SG.GROUP_ID = GM.GROUP_ID

      AND GM.CATEGORY_ID = CM.CATEGORY_ID

      AND CM.CATEGORY_ID IN ('1', '2')

      AND SG.SUB_GROUP_ID NOT IN (96, 97, 98)

      AND FD.AMOUNT < 0

      AND FM.TXN_DATE >= TO_DATE ('01-JUL-2017', 'DD-MON-YYYY')

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID NOT IN

          (SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

            FROM  TDS_SLABS_MASTER

           WHERE  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IS NOT NULL)

      AND FM.TXN_ID = FD1.TXN_ID(+)

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD1.TXN_TYPE_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD1.LOCATION_ID(+)

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD1.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID(+)

      AND am.agent_id = reg.agent_id(+)

      AND FOD.GST_AUTO_ID = GSTD.GST_AUTO_ID(+)

      AND FM.CROSS_REF = FTV.DOCUMENT_REF_NO(+)

 UNION ALL

 SELECT  FM.TXN_ID,

      FM.TXN_TYPE_ID,

      FM.LOCATION_ID,

      FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

      FM.DOCUMENT_REF_NO AS VOUCHER_NO,

      FM.TXN_DATE AS VOUCHER_DT,

      FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID,

      FAM.DESCRIPTION AS LEDGER_NAME,

      FOD.INVOICE_NUMBER,

      FOD.BILL_DATE,

      FOD.DEPT_CODE,

      DM.DEPT_NAME,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) AS INV_BASIC_AMOUNT,

      NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS TDS_AMOUNT,

      ABS (FD.AMOUNT / 100) + NVL (FD1.TDS_AMOUNT, 0) AS INV_AMOUNT,

      AM.AGENT_ID,

      'C' AS DOCUMENT_TYPE,

      'O' AS DOCUMENT_STATUS,

      reg.GSTN_NO AS JMB_GSTN_NO,

      REG.STATE_CODE AS JMB_STATE_CODE,

      REG.STATE_NAME AS JMB_STATE_NAME,

      FOD1.GST_AUTO_ID,

      GSTD.STATE_CODE AS VENDOR_STATE_CODE,

      FOD1.GSTN_NO AS VENDOR_GSTN_NO,

      FOD1.INVOICE_TYPE AS VENDOR_BILL_TYPE,

      DECODE (FOD1.SEZ_FLAG, 1, 'Y', 'N') AS VENDOR_SEZ_FLAG,

      FOD1.REG_UNREG_TYPE AS REG_OR_UNREG,

      '' AS CR_INV_DOC_REF,

      FDA.BILL_NO AS AGNST_INV_NUMBER,

      FDA.BILL_DATE AS AGNST_INV_DATE,

      GM.GROUP_ID

  FROM  FA_TXN_MASTER FM,

      FA_TXN_DETAIL FD,

      FA_TXN_OPS_DETAIL FOD,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_MASTER FAM,

      fa_dept_master dm,

      AGENT_MASTER AM,

      ( SELECT  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID,

            SUM (NVL (AMOUNT / 100, 0)) AS TDS_AMOUNT

        FROM  FA_TXN_DETAIL TEMP

        WHERE  TEMP.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IN

               ( SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID FROM TDS_SLABS_MASTER)

            AND TEMP.AMOUNT > 0

      GROUP BY  TXN_ID,

            TXN_TYPE_ID,

            ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

            LOCATION_ID) FD1,

      GST_REG_NOS reg,

      FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_GST_DTL GSTD,

      fa_sub_group_master sg,

      fa_group_master gm,

      fa_category_master cm,

      (SELECT  DISTINCT TXN_ID,

               TXN_TYPE_ID,

               ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

               LOCATION_ID,

               GST_AUTO_ID,

               GSTN_STATE_CODE,

               GSTN_NO,

               INVOICE_TYPE,

               SEZ_FLAG,

               REG_UNREG_TYPE

       FROM  FA_TXN_OPS_DETAIL TEMP1

       WHERE  TEMP1.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IN

              (SELECT  GST_INPUT FROM GST_TAX_LEDGERS

              UNION ALL

              SELECT  GST_INELIGIBLE_INPUT

               FROM  GST_TAX_LEDGERS)) FOD1,

      (SELECT  DISTINCT BILL_NO, BILL_DATE, CREDIT_NOTE_NO

       FROM  JMBTRAMP.TRAMP_FDA_CHARGE_COST_DTL) FDA

  WHERE    FM.TXN_ID = FD.TXN_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.TXN_ID = FOD.TXN_ID

      AND FD.TXN_TYPE_ID = FOD.TXN_TYPE_ID

      AND FD.LOCATION_ID = FOD.LOCATION_ID

      AND FD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FOD.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID

      AND FD.SERIAL_NO = FOD.SERIAL_NO

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID = FOD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID = FAM.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

      AND FOD.DEPT_CODE = DM.DEPT_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = AM.LOCATION_ID

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID IN ('VCRN')

      AND FAM.SUB_GROUP_ID = SG.SUB_GROUP_ID

      AND SG.GROUP_ID = GM.GROUP_ID

      AND GM.CATEGORY_ID = CM.CATEGORY_ID

      AND CM.CATEGORY_ID IN ('1', '2')

      AND SG.SUB_GROUP_ID NOT IN (96, 97, 98)

      AND FD.AMOUNT < 0

      AND FM.TXN_DATE >= TO_DATE ('01-JUL-2017', 'DD-MON-YYYY')

      AND FD.ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID NOT IN

          (SELECT  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID

            FROM  TDS_SLABS_MASTER

           WHERE  ACCOUNT_HEAD_ID IS NOT NULL)

      AND FM.TXN_ID = FD1.TXN_ID(+)

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FD1.TXN_TYPE_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FD1.LOCATION_ID(+)

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FD1.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID(+)

      AND am.agent_id = reg.agent_id(+)

      AND FOD1.GST_AUTO_ID = GSTD.GST_AUTO_ID(+)

      AND FM.TXN_ID = FOD1.TXN_ID(+)

      AND FM.TXN_TYPE_ID = FOD1.TXN_TYPE_ID(+)

      AND FM.LOCATION_ID = FOD1.LOCATION_ID(+)

      AND FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID = FOD1.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID(+)

      AND FOD.INVOICE_NUMBER = FDA.CREDIT_NOTE_NO

 UNION ALL

 SELECT  FM.TXN_ID,

      FM.TXN_TYPE_ID,

      FM.LOCATION_ID,

      FM.ACCOUNTING_YEAR_ID,

      FM.DOCUMENT_REF_NO AS VOUCHER_NO,

  FROM  FA_TXN_MASTER FM,

            LOCATION_ID) FD1,

Body:
SELECT DISTINCT

  fahm.account_head_id,

  description,

  fahgd.pob_addr,

  fahgd.email,

  fahgd.gstn_no,

  fahgd.STATE_CODE,

  LOCATION_ID

FROM

  fa_account_head_master fahm,

  fa_account_head_gst_dtl fahgd,

  FA_ACCOUNT_HEAD_DTL FAHD

WHERE

  1 = 1

  AND  fahgd.account_head_id = fahm.account_head_id

  AND  FAHD.account_head_id = fahm.account_head_id

  AND  sub_group_id = '14'

 GROUP BY fahm.account_head_id,

  description,

  fahgd.pob_addr,

  fahgd.email,

  fahgd.gstn_no,

  fahgd.STATE_CODE,

  fahgd.GST_AUTO_ID,

  LOCATION_ID

  ORDER BY DESCRIPTION ASC
